# Critical Remediation Sprint

> **Date:** 2026-03-08
> **Scope:** All critical/high issues from Phase 1 walkthrough + Phase 2 audit report
> **Result:** ALL 7 QUALITY GATES PASSED. **48/48 tests.** Zero violations.

---

## Changes Made

### Phase 2 Bugs Fixed

| Bug | File | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| Backpressure depth always 0 | [bus.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py) | Now passes `event_store.get_current_sequence()` as real depth |
| Store accepts out-of-order | [store.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/store.py) | Raises `INTEGRITY_CHECK_FAILED` on seq <= current |
| No failed routing audit | [bus.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py) | [_dispatch()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#209-230) creates `event_routing_failed` audit entry |
| ABC subscribe mismatch | [interfaces.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/interfaces.py) | Added `subscriber_id` to ABC |
| `datetime.utcnow()` | [dlq.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/dlq.py) | Uses `datetime.now(timezone.utc)` |

### Phase 2 Critical Gaps Implemented

| Gap | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Schema Registry** | [SchemaRegistry](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#17-62) class in [bus.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py) — register event types with required fields, version, content hash |
| **Signature Validation** | [compute_event_signature()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#64-73) + [verify_event_signature()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/event_bus/bus.py#75-81) — SHA-256 over event fields. All events MUST carry valid signatures |
| **system.backpressure event** | Audit entry emitted when backpressure activates |

### Phase 1 Critical Gaps Implemented

| Gap | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Identity Lifecycle** | [IdentityStatus](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py#15-21) enum + [suspend_identity()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py#116-126), [reinstate_identity()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py#127-147), [revoke_identity()](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py#148-162) in [service.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/identity/service.py) — all audited |
| **Module Sandbox** | Restricted builtins execution in [loader.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/module_loader/loader.py) — strips `__import__`, `exec`, [eval](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/interfaces.py#46-51), `compile`, `open`, `getattr`, `globals` |

